{
  "info": {
    "name": "Controle Financeiro API",
    "description": "API do sistema Controle Financeiro\n\n## Base URL\n`{{base_url}}` (default: `http://localhost:8082`)\n\n## Autenticação\n- **API Key**: Enviar via header `Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}` ou query param `?api_key={{api_key}}`\n- **Session**: Fazer login via `/authenticate` e usar cookie de sessão\n\n## Fluxo de uso\n1. Execute **Login** → recebe código por email\n2. Execute **Verificar Código 2FA** com o código recebido\n3. Use qualquer endpoint protegido\n\n> ✅ Todos os endpoints retornam JSON formatado.\n> ✅ Endpoints com `Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}` não precisam de login (exceto criação de transações que precisa do `user_email` da sessão).",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "controle-financeiro"
  },
  "event": [
    {
      "listen": "prerequest",
      "script": {
        "exec": [
          "const skipPaths = ['/authenticate','/verify_token','/register','/forgot_password','/reset_password','/logout'];",
          "const reqPath = pm.request.url.getPath();",
          "const shouldSkip = skipPaths.some(p => reqPath.startsWith(p));",
          "if (shouldSkip) return;",
          "",
          "if (reqPath.startsWith('/api/')) {",
          "  const hasAuth = pm.request.headers.one('Authorization');",
          "  if (hasAuth && hasAuth.value.includes('Bearer')) return;",
          "  console.warn('⚠️  Endpoint API sem API Key. Adicione header: Authorization: Bearer {{api_key}}');",
          "  return;",
          "}",
          "",
          "const authed = pm.collectionVariables.get('session_valid') === 'true';",
          "if (authed) return;",
          "const hasCookie = pm.cookies.has('rack.session');",
          "if (hasCookie) { pm.collectionVariables.set('session_valid', 'true'); return; }",
          "",
          "console.warn('⚠️  Sessão não encontrada. Tentando login automático...');",
          "const loginUrl = pm.collectionVariables.get('base_url') || pm.variables.get('base_url');",
          "pm.sendRequest({",
          "  url: loginUrl + '/authenticate',",
          "  method: 'POST',",
          "  header: { 'Content-Type': 'application/x-www-form-urlencoded' },",
          "  body: {",
          "    mode: 'urlencoded',",
          "    urlencoded: [",
          "      { key: 'email', value: pm.collectionVariables.get('email') || '' },",
          "      { key: 'password', value: pm.collectionVariables.get('password') || '' }",
          "    ]",
          "  }",
          "}, function (err, res) {",
          "  if (err) { console.error('❌  Erro no login automático:', err); return; }",
          "  if (res.code === 200) {",
          "    console.warn('📧  Login OK! Código 2FA enviado. Execute \"Verificar Código 2FA\" com o código recebido.');",
          "  } else {",
          "    console.error('❌  Login automático falhou. Execute o fluxo manual.');",
          "  }",
          "});"
        ],
        "type": "text/javascript"
      }
    },
    {
      "listen": "test",
      "script": {
        "exec": [
          "if (pm.response.code === 302 && pm.response.headers.get('Location') !== '/login') {",
          "  pm.collectionVariables.set('session_valid', 'true');",
          "}",
          "if (pm.response.code === 403) {",
          "  console.error('❌  Acesso negado. Verifique se a API Key está correta ou se a sessão está ativa.');",
          "}"
        ],
        "type": "text/javascript"
      }
    }
  ],
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Autenticação",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Login",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded" }],
            "body": { "mode": "urlencoded", "urlencoded": [
              { "key": "email", "value": "{{email}}" },
              { "key": "password", "value": "{{password}}" }
            ]},
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/authenticate", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["authenticate"] }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 200) {",
                  "  console.log('✅  Login OK! Verifique seu email para pegar o código 2FA.');",
                  "} else {",
                  "  console.error('❌  Login falhou. Verifique email e senha.');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Sucesso",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "text/html;charset=utf-8" }]
            },
            {
              "name": "Credenciais inválidas",
              "code": 401,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "text/html;charset=utf-8" }]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Verificar Código 2FA",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded" }],
            "body": { "mode": "urlencoded", "urlencoded": [
              { "key": "code", "value": "{{verification_code}}" }
            ]},
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/verify_token", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["verify_token"] }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "if (pm.response.code === 302) {",
                  "  pm.collectionVariables.set('session_valid', 'true');",
                  "  console.log('✅  Autenticado!');",
                  "} else {",
                  "  console.error('❌  Código inválido.');",
                  "}"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Sucesso",
              "code": 302,
              "header": [{ "key": "Location", "value": "/" }]
            },
            {
              "name": "Código inválido",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "text/html;charset=utf-8" }]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Solicitar Cadastro",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded" }],
            "body": { "mode": "urlencoded", "urlencoded": [
              { "key": "email", "value": "{{new_email}}" }
            ]},
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/register", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["register"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Confirmar Cadastro (GET)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/register/{{registration_token}}", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["register", "{{registration_token}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Definir Senha (POST)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded" }],
            "body": { "mode": "urlencoded", "urlencoded": [
              { "key": "username", "value": "{{username}}" },
              { "key": "password", "value": "{{new_password}}" },
              { "key": "confirm_password", "value": "{{new_password}}" }
            ]},
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/register/{{registration_token}}", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["register", "{{registration_token}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Esqueci Senha",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded" }],
            "body": { "mode": "urlencoded", "urlencoded": [
              { "key": "email", "value": "{{email}}" }
            ]},
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/forgot_password", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["forgot_password"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Redefinir Senha (GET)",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/reset_password/{{reset_token}}", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["reset_password", "{{reset_token}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Redefinir Senha (POST)",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded" }],
            "body": { "mode": "urlencoded", "urlencoded": [
              { "key": "password", "value": "{{new_password}}" },
              { "key": "confirm_password", "value": "{{new_password}}" }
            ]},
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/reset_password/{{reset_token}}", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["reset_password", "{{reset_token}}"] }
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "Logout",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/logout", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["logout"] }
          },
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('session_valid', 'false');",
                  "console.log('🔓  Sessão encerrada.');"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "API (JSON)",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "Listar Usuários",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{api_key}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/users", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "users"] }
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Sucesso",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "[\n  {\n    \"email\": \"admin@exemplo.com\",\n    \"username\": \"Admin\",\n    \"admin\": true,\n    \"created_at\": \"2026-05-28T03:29:27+00:00\"\n  }\n]"
            },
            {
              "name": "Acesso Negado",
              "code": 403,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\"error\": \"Acesso negado\"}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Listar Transações",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{api_key}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/transactions?start_date={{start_date}}&end_date={{end_date}}",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "transactions"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "start_date", "value": "{{start_date}}" },
                { "key": "end_date", "value": "{{end_date}}" },
                { "key": "filter_type", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "filter_category", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "filter_desc", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "page", "value": "1", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "per_page", "value": "23", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "user", "value": "", "disabled": true }
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Sucesso",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"page\": 1,\n  \"per_page\": 23,\n  \"total\": 42,\n  \"total_pages\": 2,\n  \"data\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": 1,\n      \"transaction_date\": \"2026-05-28\",\n      \"description\": \"Supermercado\",\n      \"amount\": 150.50,\n      \"transaction_type\": \"Gasto\",\n      \"category\": \"Alimentação\",\n      \"payment_method\": \"Pix\",\n      \"status\": \"Pendente\",\n      \"installments\": null,\n      \"due_date\": null,\n      \"user_email\": \"user@email.com\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Acesso Negado",
              "code": 403,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\"error\": \"Acesso negado\"}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Criar Transação",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{api_key}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"transaction_date\": \"{{transaction_date}}\",\n  \"description\": \"{{description}}\",\n  \"amount\": {{amount}},\n  \"transaction_type\": \"{{transaction_type}}\",\n  \"category\": \"{{category}}\",\n  \"payment_method\": \"{{payment_method}}\",\n  \"status\": \"Pendente\"\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/transactions", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "transactions"] }
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Criado",
              "code": 201,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"id\": 10,\n  \"transaction_date\": \"2026-05-28\",\n  \"description\": \"Nova transação\",\n  \"amount\": 100.0,\n  \"transaction_type\": \"Gasto\",\n  \"category\": \"Alimentação\",\n  \"payment_method\": \"Pix\",\n  \"status\": \"Pendente\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Acesso Negado",
              "code": 403,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\"error\": \"Acesso negado\"}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Atualizar Transação",
          "request": {
            "method": "PATCH",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{api_key}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"description\": \"{{description}} atualizado\",\n  \"amount\": {{amount}}\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/transactions/{{transaction_id}}", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "transactions", "{{transaction_id}}"] }
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Sucesso",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"id\": 1,\n  \"description\": \"Nova transação atualizado\",\n  \"amount\": 100.0,\n  \"status\": \"Pendente\"\n}"
            },
            {
              "name": "Não encontrada",
              "code": 404,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\"error\": \"Transação não encontrada\"}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Excluir Transação",
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{api_key}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/transactions/{{transaction_id}}", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "transactions", "{{transaction_id}}"] }
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Sucesso",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\"message\": \"Transação excluída\"}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Excluir em Lote",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{api_key}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }
            ],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"ids\": [1, 2, 3]\n}"
            },
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/transactions/bulk_delete", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "transactions", "bulk_delete"] }
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Sucesso",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\"message\": \"3 transação(ões) excluída(s)\", \"deleted\": 3}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Alternar Status",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{api_key}}" }],
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/transactions/{{transaction_id}}/toggle_status", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "transactions", "{{transaction_id}}", "toggle_status"] }
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Sucesso",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"id\": 1,\n  \"status\": \"Pago\",\n  \"description\": \"Supermercado\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Alternar Parcela",
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [
              { "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{api_key}}" },
              { "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/x-www-form-urlencoded" }
            ],
            "body": { "mode": "urlencoded", "urlencoded": [
              { "key": "installment", "value": "1" }
            ]},
            "url": { "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/transactions/{{transaction_id}}/toggle_installment", "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "transactions", "{{transaction_id}}", "toggle_installment"] }
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Sucesso",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"id\": 1,\n  \"paid_installments\": [1],\n  \"installments\": 3\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "Dashboard Dívidas",
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [{ "key": "Authorization", "value": "Bearer {{api_key}}" }],
            "url": {
              "raw": "{{base_url}}/api/dashboard",
              "host": ["{{base_url}}"], "path": ["api", "dashboard"],
              "query": [
                { "key": "filter_type", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "filter_desc", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "filter_status", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "filter_vencimento", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "filter_valor", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "filter_vencimento_start", "value": "", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "page", "value": "1", "disabled": true },
                { "key": "per_page", "value": "23", "disabled": true }
              ]
            }
          },
          "response": [
            {
              "name": "Sucesso",
              "code": 200,
              "header": [{ "key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json" }],
              "body": "{\n  \"page\": 1,\n  \"per_page\": 23,\n  \"total\": 5,\n  \"total_pages\": 1,\n  \"total_paid\": 500.0,\n  \"total_remaining\": 1200.0,\n  \"data\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": 1,\n      \"description\": \"Financiamento Carro (Parcela 1 de 24)\",\n      \"amount\": 850.0,\n      \"due_date\": \"2026-06-15\",\n      \"is_paid\": false,\n      \"vencimento_status\": \"Em dia\"\n    }\n  ]\n}"
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
